</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>ptr2</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The pointer to the second memory region to compare </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>n</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The number of bytes to compare </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>0 if the first n bytes of ptr1 and ptr 2 match. Otherwise, the sign is determined by the sign of the difference between the first pair of bytes that differ in ptr1 and ptr2. </para>
